## 4. Component Requirements

### 4.1 Core Components (P0 - This Task)

| Component | Variants | Props | Accessibility |
|-----------|----------|-------|---------------|
| **Button** | `default`, `secondary`, `outline`, `ghost`, `destructive`, `link` | `size`, `disabled`, `loading`, `asChild` | Focus ring, aria-disabled |
| **Input** | Text, Password, Search | `type`, `placeholder`, `disabled`, `error` | aria-invalid, aria-describedby |
| **Textarea** | Default | `rows`, `placeholder`, `disabled` | aria-invalid |
| **Card** | Default | `children`, `className` | Semantic HTML |
| **Avatar** | `xs`, `sm`, `md`, `lg`, `xl` | `src`, `alt`, `fallback` | alt text required |
| **Badge** | `default`, `secondary`, `destructive`, `outline` | `variant` | role="status" where needed |
| **Dialog/Modal** | Default, Full, Bottom Sheet | `open`, `onOpenChange` | Focus trap, escape key |
| **Toast** | `default`, `success`, `error`, `warning` | `title`, `description`, `action` | aria-live, role="alert" |
| **Tabs** | Default, Pills | `value`, `onValueChange` | aria-selected, keyboard nav |
| **Select** | Default | `value`, `onValueChange`, `options` | aria-expanded, keyboard nav |
| **Dropdown Menu** | Default | `trigger`, `items` | aria-haspopup, keyboard nav |
| **Skeleton** | Text, Circle, Card | `className` | aria-hidden |
| **Label** | Default | `htmlFor` | Associated with input |
| **Separator** | Horizontal, Vertical | `orientation` | role="separator" |

